   {
      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Concept ACK. For files that need it, I think it makes sense to be able to include just `cs_main` without having to know its signature or pull in a header that thinks it knows it.\r\n\r\nAnd giving it a home in its own compilation unit means that we no longer have to pull in the arbitrary object where it resides just to get it linked. So I think this is a nice cleanup. ",
